<li><i><a href="../../w/index-title=Portrait_of_Baudouin_de_Lannoy&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Portrait of Baudouin de Lannoy (page does not exist)">Portrait of Baudouin de Lannoy</a></i> (c. 1435)</li>
<li><i><a href="../../w/index-title=Portrait_of_a_Man_with_Carnation&action=edit&redlink=1.php.html" class="new" title="Portrait of a Man with Carnation (page does not exist)">Portrait of a Man with Carnation</a></i> (1435)</li>
