<div><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Portrait of a Man by Jan van Eyck-small.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/100px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg" width="100" height="137" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/150px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8b/Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg/200px-Portrait_of_a_Man_by_Jan_van_Eyck-small.jpg 2x" /></a></div>
</td>
